Señor Bai,

00:26:59.790 --> 00:27:01.120
Vamos adentro a hablar.

00:27:11.570 --> 00:27:12.240
¡Señor Bai!

00:27:20.290 --> 00:27:23.320
[Ciudad de Liuhu]

00:27:57.830 --> 00:27:58.680
Bochas.

